data.title: SVOD 2014 - Silicon Valley Open Doors Investment Conference
data.meta_description:
It has been 10 years since SVOD opened its doors for the first time to the amazing Silicon Valley community of technology entrepreneurs and investors, and we are now ready to celebrate the achievement with the biggest conference yet. 
    
    Join us to celebrate our special 10th Anniversary SVOD Conference on June 11-12, 2014 at the Computer History Museum, in Silicon Valley. As always, there will be plenty of opportunities to network, pitch your startup, find an investment target, build partnerships and so much more.
    
    As our fellow SVOD Conference alums, you are the first to receive this special invitation to the 10th Anniversary SVOD, and we are thrilled to offer you the registration at a hugely discounted price. The number of discounted tickets is limited, so do not miss this opportunity!
    
    We are looking forward to welcoming you to the 10th Anniversary SVOD Conference and to our circle of friends from the Silicon Valley and beyond!
